WEBVTT

00:09.302 --> 00:12.294
What the fuck do you mean,
you don't want it?

00:12.513 --> 00:15.755
-Jessioa--
-Why, Bill?

00:15.933 --> 00:17.514
You don't even know, do you?

00:17.685 --> 00:20.347
I don't know how to explain myself...

00:20.521 --> 00:22.853
...other than to say
that I have accepted my fate.

00:23.024 --> 00:26.437
And that would be all well and good
if you had to, but you don't, right?

00:26.611 --> 00:28.897
All you've gotta do
is drink this cunt's blood...

00:29.071 --> 00:30.481
...and this could all be over.

00:30.698 --> 00:31.858
[MUFFLED SHOUTING]

00:32.033 --> 00:34.900
As much as I appreciate
a compelling character drama...

00:35.077 --> 00:36.578
...the yakuza are upstairs...

00:36.746 --> 00:40.330
...so need I remind you to
keep it the fuck down volume-wise?

00:40.875 --> 00:44.038
Whatever this is, whatever you're doing...

00:44.212 --> 00:47.329
...you don't get to hide
behind the word "fate."

00:47.506 --> 00:49.838
The cure is right fucking there.

00:50.009 --> 00:52.625
Look at her. She's your fate.

00:52.803 --> 00:55.294
She is your destiny.

00:55.806 --> 00:58.218
If you don't drink her blood...

00:58.392 --> 01:00.644
...you're making a choice, Bill.

01:00.811 --> 01:02.938
A choice you won't have to live with...

01:03.481 --> 01:06.314
...but we will, Jessica and me.

01:08.694 --> 01:09.729
You're right.

01:10.821 --> 01:12.277
Thank God.

01:12.448 --> 01:14.734
I am making a choice.

01:16.911 --> 01:20.199
I'm choosing the true death.

01:24.043 --> 01:27.080
-Fuck you, Bill.
BILL: Jessica.

01:32.301 --> 01:34.257
SOOKIE:
Don't you look at me like that.

01:34.428 --> 01:38.012
I'm with her. I want to know why.

01:38.182 --> 01:40.138
I can't.

01:42.353 --> 01:44.059
Try!

01:45.273 --> 01:46.638
There are no words.

01:52.154 --> 01:53.815
You should leave.

01:54.991 --> 01:58.199
And not a word about Sarah to anyone.

01:58.369 --> 02:00.280
I understand.

02:06.585 --> 02:08.121
Bill?

02:10.131 --> 02:11.871
I want you to release me.

02:12.049 --> 02:14.335
-Jessica--
-Do it.

02:26.522 --> 02:28.137
Jessica Hamby...

02:29.859 --> 02:32.191
...as I know you know...

02:33.612 --> 02:35.898
...I never wanted to make you a vampire.

02:36.782 --> 02:38.738
Turning you was punishment...

02:39.368 --> 02:42.360
...for taking the life of one of our kind.

02:45.875 --> 02:47.661
lam so proud...

02:48.878 --> 02:50.869
...of the vampire that you've become...

02:52.256 --> 02:56.340
...and I know you will stand out there
on your own two feet...

02:57.219 --> 03:00.427
...just beautifully when I am gone.

03:03.976 --> 03:07.719
l renounce the ties of our blood...

03:08.814 --> 03:12.352
...and my dominion
over you as my progeny.

03:14.862 --> 03:17.569
As your maker, Jessica...

03:18.824 --> 03:20.689
...I release you.

03:31.337 --> 03:33.328
[SOBBING]

03:42.223 --> 03:46.136
Cry on my jacket,
you're paying for it, sweetheart.

03:47.520 --> 03:48.851
I'm sorry, Sookie.

03:49.021 --> 03:51.228
[SOBBING]

05:39.423 --> 05:40.629
It's safe.

05:40.799 --> 05:42.505
-You can come on out.
SOOKIE: Thanks.

05:54.104 --> 05:57.562
-Where'd you go, Sam?
-Sookie?

06:11.038 --> 06:13.199
Do you want me to wait outside?

06:14.166 --> 06:16.452
Actually, I don't wanna be alone.

06:24.009 --> 06:27.046
"Dearest Sookie,
if you're reading this letter...

06:27.221 --> 06:30.509
