06:38.649 --> 06:40.685
-Thanks, sweetie.
-Ah. No problem.

06:40.859 --> 06:43.236
-This little girl's doing backflips in here.
-Yeah?

06:43.404 --> 06:45.315
SAM:
And she says we 're all crazy.

06:45.489 --> 06:51.576
I think we might just be resilient.
Either way, there are two things I am sure of.

06:51.745 --> 06:54.407
The ﬁrst is that I love Nico/e very much.

06:54.582 --> 06:57.324
-Hey, hey, hey, no fucking way, baby.
-I got it.

06:57.501 --> 06:59.332
-You don't got it.
-I almost had it.

06:59.503 --> 07:02.495
-Yeah, you did almost have it. Jeez.
-l'm still strong, you know?

07:02.673 --> 07:06.131
I know you're strong, but you gotta relax.
Come on, why don't you sit down?

07:06.302 --> 07:10.215
The second is there ain't no way I’m gonna
