08:15.746 --> 08:19.364
SOOKIE: Arlene? Knock-knock.
-Sookie, is that you?

08:19.541 --> 08:21.668
Yeah, I didn't wanna sneak up on you.

08:21.835 --> 08:23.541
-I brought Jessica with.
ARLENE: Yay.

08:26.340 --> 08:28.046
Well, this shouldn't be weird at all.

08:29.510 --> 08:31.046
-Hey, Redbone.
-Hey.

08:31.595 --> 08:34.052
What's going on here?

08:34.223 --> 08:35.929
-Did you see Field of Dreams?
-No.

08:36.100 --> 08:37.840
Say it, Big John.

08:38.018 --> 08:39.758
"If you build it, they will come."

08:39.937 --> 08:42.428
-Yes, they will.
-I don't get it.

08:42.606 --> 08:45.564
Well, the way I see it,
business sucks right now...

08:45.734 --> 08:50.068
...but it ain't ever gonna
pick up unless we open up.

08:50.239 --> 08:53.982
So I decided that starting tonight,
we're just gonna show up for work anyhow...

08:54.159 --> 08:57.151
...then just wait it out
till the customers start coming back.

08:57.329 --> 08:58.705
But in the meantime...

08:58.872 --> 09:02.239
...party's gonna have to be just for us, y'all.

09:02.459 --> 09:03.835
