09:06.964 --> 09:08.750
No, thanks. Not right now.

09:11.468 --> 09:13.129
ls you all right, Sook?

09:13.303 --> 09:15.294
Sam's gone.

09:15.806 --> 09:18.593
-What?
SOOKIE: He's gone.

09:18.767 --> 09:20.507
Can I talk to you for a sec?

09:33.031 --> 09:34.407
What's going on?

