09:39.037 --> 09:40.538
I found them in his trailer.

09:41.081 --> 09:42.287
Okay.

09:42.458 --> 09:44.244
Mine was pretty heavy, so I figured...

09:44.752 --> 09:48.085
...you might not wanna read it
in front of a whole bunch of people.

09:48.255 --> 09:50.587
Yeah, yeah, this is
probably more appropriate...

09:50.758 --> 09:52.749
...considering the circumstances.
Thank you.

09:52.926 --> 09:56.293
-Do you want to be alone?
-No, sweetheart. You can stay.

10:05.147 --> 10:06.808
Andy?

10:07.274 --> 10:09.686
"Dear Sheriff Bellefleur, l resign.

10:09.860 --> 10:12.272
Sincerely, Sam Merlotte."

10:12.446 --> 10:13.936
-That's it?
-That's it.

10:14.114 --> 10:15.979
So the whole closed-door thing?

10:16.575 --> 10:19.282
Completely unnecessary.

10:19.495 --> 10:20.826
[CHATTERING]

