I know in this town...

19:09.649 --> 19:13.562
-...so do you think you could come and get me?
-Sure, but who is this?

19:13.987 --> 19:16.603
It's me, Brigette.

19:16.781 --> 19:17.941
Hoyt's Brigette?

19:19.367 --> 19:21.153
