19:21.328 --> 19:22.943
Oh, shit. What happened?

19:23.121 --> 19:25.863
Well, that redheaded vampire
from last night showed up and--

19:26.041 --> 19:27.622
Whoa, whoa, whoa, Jessica?

19:27.792 --> 19:30.078
